… Local, State, National delegates congreses hold 12th-14th May  BY BENEDICT NWACHUKWU, ABUJA The All Progressives Congress (APC) National Working Committee (NWC) has extended the party’s sale of Expression of Interest and Nomination Forms for the 2023 General Elections to Tuesday, May 10, 2022. A terse statement on Monday signed by the party’s National Publicity Secretary, Felix Morka, reads:
“In a revised timetable issued by the APC National Organising Secretary, Sulaiman Muhammad Argungu, the last day for submission of completed forms and accompanying documents is now set for Wednesday, 11th May. “In same vein, Congresses to elect Local Government Area (LGA), State and National Delegates will now hold from Thursday, 12th May to Saturday, 14th May, 2022.” 